An original painting of Bob Marley, digitized then professionally printed direct to garment.

White Ladies (Left) or Mens (Right) Tank Top, also available in Grey.
 - 100% ringspun cotton 
 - Fitted style with side seams
 - Rib bound neck and armholes
 - Twin needle hem 

Size Guide: 
S- 8/10  
M- 10/12  
L- 12/14           
XL- 14/16  
XXL- 16/18

Mens Size Guide:
S- 35/37 Inch Chest
M- 38/40 Inch Chest
L- 41/43 Inch Chest
XL- 44/46 Inch Chest
XXL- 47/49 Inch Chest
